In this application, when the user visits the website , he or she may regiser as a new user or login to continue as a existing user.
If he wishes to login, then the user details are carried to a servlet where validation is done against provided credentials. 
If the user wishes to register, then a registration form is displayed and the user needs to get registered with the required fields. 
If he or she provides valid details,then an account will be created by a jsp page with the back of java beans at the back end and the 
details are added to the database through java beans. Now the user logins.
